column16:
The intervention undoubtedly made the streets around the Centro Cultural do Dragão more inviting.
The presence of the police is another important point in Brazil, which prevents crime.
Over time, trees planted in pots will grow and provide shade to make the environment even more pleasant. 
The only point that would improve would be to change the position of the benches on the other side of the street, which face the facade, to the square.
